OL,3,CWhat is the difference between legal,
OL,4,Cillegal and irregular migration?
OL,6,FThe Government has vowed one of its
OL,7,Ftop priorities is to stop illegal
OL,8,Fmigration, with US President Donald
OL,9,FTrump even wading into the debate to
OL,10,Fsay an option would be to call in the
OL,11,Fmilitary.
OL,13,FHere, the PA news agency takes a look
OL,14,Fat some of the language around the
OL,15,Fissue, including the difference
OL,16,Fbetween legal and illegal migration.
OL,18,F` What is migration?
