OL,3,CWhat is the difference between legal,
OL,4,Cillegal and irregular migration?
OL,6,FYes. Most people come here on a visa
OL,7,For through one of the Government's
OL,8,Fhumanitarian routes, such as a
OL,9,Fresettlement scheme.
OL,11,FMost of the people who immigrated to
OL,12,Fthe UK in 2024 were from outside what
OL,13,Fis known as the EU+ area (the European
OL,14,FUnion, plus Norway, Iceland,
OL,15,FLiechtenstein and Switzerland) and the
OL,16,FONS publishes a breakdown of the
OL,17,Freasons these people came to the UK.
