OL,3,CWhat is the difference between legal,
OL,4,Cillegal and irregular migration?
OL,6,FOf the 766,000 non EU+ nationals who
OL,7,Fimmigrated to the country in 2024, 35%
OL,8,Farrived on a study visa; 34% on a work
OL,9,Fvisa; 10% on a family visa (joining
OL,10,Frelatives or partners who already have
OL,11,Fsettled status in the UK); and 7%
OL,12,Farrived via a humanitarian route.
OL,14,FExamples of recent humanitarian routes
OL,15,Finclude the Afghan and Ukraine
OL,16,Fresettlement schemes, and the route
OL,17,Ffor eligible British nationals wishing
OL,18,Fto relocate from Hong Kong.
