OL,6,FJust 12% of non EU+ nationals who
OL,7,Fimmigrated to the UK in 2024 were
OL,8,Fclassed as people who had applied for
OL,9,Fasylum within a year of arriving in
OL,10,Fthe UK, either via a regular route `
OL,11,Fhaving previously arrived legally on a
