OL,3,CWhat is the difference between legal,
OL,4,Cillegal and irregular migration?
OL,6,FAnyone seeking international
OL,7,Fprotection from war, persecution and
OL,8,Fhuman rights violations can apply for
OL,9,Fasylum in the UK.
OL,11,FA person who has been granted the
OL,12,Fright to asylum in the UK is then
OL,13,Fclassed as having refugee status in
OL,14,Fthe country.
