OL,3,CWhat is the difference between legal,
OL,4,Cillegal and irregular migration?
OL,6,FTo stay in the UK as a refugee, you
OL,7,Fmust demonstrate that you are unable
OL,8,Fto live safely in any part of your own
OL,9,Fcountry because of fear of persecution
OL,10,Fbecause of your race, religion,
OL,11,Fnationality, political opinion or
OL,12,Fother factors which might put you at
OL,13,Frisk such as gender, gender identity
OL,14,For sexual orientation.
OL,16,FNot all asylum seekers will become
OL,17,Frefugees as some will have their claim
OL,18,Frefused.
OL,20,FHowever, all refugees have previously
OL,21,Fbeen asylum seekers.
