OL,3,CWhat is the difference between legal,
OL,4,Cillegal and irregular migration?
OL,6,F` Is it illegal to come to the UK to
OL,7,Fseek asylum?
OL,9,FIt is not illegal to seek asylum in
OL,10,Fthe UK but it is a criminal offence in
OL,11,Fthe UK to enter the country without
OL,12,Fpermission.
OL,14,FThere is no asylum visa to come to the
OL,15,FUK specifically for the purpose to
OL,16,Fclaim asylum, however, you must be
OL,17,Fphysically in the UK to apply for
OL,18,Frefugee status.
